-- DaimlerChrysler supervisory board names Bischoff chairman
-- 
-- Wed Apr 4, 2007 6:14pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/04/04/us-daimlerchrysler-chairman-idUSWNAS569320070404

 

 (Reuters) - DaimlerChrysler AG DCX.N said its supervisory board elected Manfred Bischoff, the chairman of EADS ( EAD.PA ), as its new chairman effective immediately, succeeding Hilmar Kopper. 

 The company's shareholders also approved the distribution of a dividend of $2.002 per share for 2006, DaimlerChrysler said in a statement. (Reporting by Hari Kumar in Bangalore)